graph LR
    ModelMesh[ModelMesh Serving<br/>Operator]

    %% External Dependencies - Required
    ModelMesh -->|required<br/>state coordination| etcd[etcd v3.5.4+<br/>Distributed State]
    ModelMesh -->|required<br/>model storage| S3[S3/MinIO<br/>Object Storage]
    ModelMesh -->|required<br/>core runtime| ModelMeshRuntime[modelmesh v0.11.2<br/>Core Runtime]
    ModelMesh -->|required<br/>model pulling| RuntimeAdapter[modelmesh-runtime-adapter<br/>v0.11.2]

    %% External Dependencies - Optional Model Servers
    ModelMesh -.->|optional<br/>inference runtime| Triton[Triton Inference Server 2.x<br/>TensorFlow/PyTorch/ONNX]
    ModelMesh -.->|optional<br/>inference runtime| MLServer[MLServer 1.x<br/>scikit-learn/XGBoost]
    ModelMesh -.->|optional<br/>inference runtime| OpenVINO[OpenVINO Model Server 1.x<br/>Intel Optimized]
    ModelMesh -.->|optional<br/>inference runtime| TorchServe[TorchServe 0.x<br/>PyTorch Native]
    ModelMesh -.->|optional<br/>REST support| RestProxy[rest-proxy v0.11.2<br/>KServe V2 REST]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies - Optional
    ModelMesh -.->|optional<br/>mTLS & traffic mgmt| Istio[Service Mesh - Istio<br/>mTLS]
    ModelMesh -.->|optional<br/>metrics collection| PrometheusOp[Prometheus Operator<br/>ServiceMonitor]
    ModelMesh -.->|optional<br/>webhook certs| CertManager[cert-manager 1.13+<br/>Certificate API]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard[ODH Dashboard] -.->|UI management| ModelMesh
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -.->|automated deployment| ModelMesh

    %% Core Platform
    ModelMesh -->|CRD operations<br/>watch & reconcile| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS]

